{"tid":1887278,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【本土研究社】隔離營唔駛用公屋嘅，叫啲狗嘔返啲渡假營出黎先啦","createTime":"2020-02-19T12:04:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-22T12:40:05.000Z","uid":138409,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"a473c36d1cf91eff81c09d69cea15ef6b7d9bdcc","tid":1887278,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T12:04:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/localresearch/posts/2857517354344319\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flocalresearch%2Fposts%2F2857517354344319&d=lLWZrBwjloX75B4v2mFt5IbsTeectjBlsojPGUwt5kI%3D&h=9e5cb980\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/localresearch/posts/2857517354344319</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ER1r7aG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FER1r7aG.jpg&h=32dff975&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/96X3pXn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F96X3pXn.jpg&h=86ffe84e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n0XSiho.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn0XSiho.jpg&h=0d28aa98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J6oNRCp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ6oNRCp.jpg&h=49fa92f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gvgvPo5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgvgvPo5.jpg&h=1b01ba7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GPW39o5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGPW39o5.jpg&h=5b3afa98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【隔離營隱藏選項：洞梓警察渡假屋】<br />\n研究員剛在田野考察過程中，發現有個隱世渡假營相當適合做隔離營，叫洞梓警察渡假屋，請大家幫手推介一下。<br />\n<br />\n渡假屋位處大埔洞梓路到盡頭，<span style=\"color: gold;\">人煙稀少</span>，營內屋與屋間隔適中，每間渡假屋都上千呎，廚房廁所、燒烤爐、娛樂設施一應俱全，之前還有麻雀供應，面對大埔慈山寺觀音像景，風水好過火神山，相當適合做隔離營。<br />\n<br />\n不要被官方資料影響，誤以為裡面只得5間度假大屋可租【註一】，做隔離營空間有限。<span style=\"color: gold;\">實地可見，其實另一邊重收埋左十多個門牌 (B1-B5、B8-B12及C2-C5)大屋，長期丟空，又唔翻新，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">現時放在可供短租政府土地表無人問津</span>。</span><br />\n<br />\n翻查官方紀錄，揭示該度假營亦<span style=\"color: gold;\">曾於2014年用作跨部門伊波拉病毒防疫演習，與當時與鯉魚門公園同時被徵用作模擬感染病毒後的防疫訓練。</span>【註二】現時鯉魚門公園已被徵用作隔離營，但警察度假屋卻依然固我。<br />\n<br />\n去年警隊還為渡假屋重開舉辦過一場度假屋命名大賽，最後得獎名稱叫梓藍、梓樂、梓然、梓雅及梓和【註三】，反映了現時警隊的創意水平。如果徵用做隔離營，大家又會幫佢改個咩名?<br />\n<br />\n其實政府連自己設施都未善用好，又不肯全面封關，就要徵用社區公屋戶埋單，根本說不過去，應倡議立即徵用度假營及翻新丟空度假屋做隔離營，相關部門亦不要在疫情當前還漠視未善用官地。<br />\n<br />\n#田野考察<br />\n#未善用官地<br />\n#洞梓警察渡假屋<br />\n#渡假屋叫梓樂<br />\n#虧你重住得落<br />\n<br />\n--<br />\n【註一】《警聲》- 健康生活：洞梓警察度假屋重新開放<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.police.gov.hk/offbeat/1129/chi/7661.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Foffbeat%2F1129%2Fchi%2F7661.html&d=lLWZrBwjloX75B4v2mFt5IbsTeectjBlsojPGUwt5kI%3D&h=5c1969dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.police.gov.hk/offbeat/1129/chi/7661.html</a><br />\n<br />\n【註二】2015年衛生防護中心《通訊》第三十六期 p.7<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.chp.gov.hk/files/pdf/chp36_en.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chp.gov.hk%2Ffiles%2Fpdf%2Fchp36_en.pdf&d=lLWZrBwjloX75B4v2mFt5IbsTeectjBlsojPGUwt5kI%3D&h=17b3bdc7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.chp.gov.hk/files/pdf/chp36_en.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n【註三】《警聲》- 簡訊：洞梓警察度假屋命名比賽頒獎典禮<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.police.gov.hk/offbeat/1132/chi/7813.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Foffbeat%2F1132%2Fchi%2F7813.html&d=lLWZrBwjloX75B4v2mFt5IbsTeectjBlsojPGUwt5kI%3D&h=86661b58\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.police.gov.hk/offbeat/1132/chi/7813.html</a><br />\n<br />\n--<br />\n💰挖多啲地 支持民間土地研究：<br />\n<a href=\"https://liber-research.com/research-category/land-supply/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fliber-research.com%2Fresearch-category%2Fland-supply%2F&d=lLWZrBwjloX75B4v2mFt5IbsTeectjBlsojPGUwt5kI%3D&h=6b9da914\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://liber-research.com/research-category/land-supply/</a>"},{"pid":"2483e289c8afd93bbc9a5d1d8b9383b123728cea","tid":1887278,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T12:07:10.000Z","msg":"啲大sir要用呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c3dd74d3f949587f5f6c4e96d925e3e6aeabb05","tid":1887278,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T12:07:41.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"84bf6d1b863a75bc3ff52798edc4f46ed3eb824b","tid":1887278,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T12:08:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a5ef5e4598ebde5c93f396d0617b89fe8f9d3507","tid":1887278,"uid":286309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T12:09:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d9897a0a89784f9cc1a75e58c7c180ae0ff32b6d","tid":1887278,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2483e289c8afd93bbc9a5d1d8b9383b123728cea","tid":1887278,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T12:07:10.000Z","msg":"啲大sir要用呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T12:09:07.000Z","msg":"沙公安表示帶女返狗屋屌過引過係渡假營"},{"pid":"bcf31fc9fcd7673713c26518595fc0cccd36973b","tid":1887278,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T12:10:21.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"821f11203195091262224195378803e1aa50a3d0","tid":1887278,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T12:10:45.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c4e3cec23ba70fb0481ede473dfc3c32815fe28b","tid":1887278,"uid":196053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T12:11:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f9c92023350222198bfb8c0c37571d4c4c9e7056","tid":1887278,"uid":99964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T12:11:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6f63f347235708dea78f311528de67b6dc57c0f5","tid":1